attributes.name: Bloom | 0.5g Live Surf | Grape Soda
attributes.body: "Grape Soda Enjoy the worry-free mellow mood of Grape Soda at home. This strain has a strong indica dominance, so it's perfect for a solo night in, like taking an online yoga class and watching a good movie. Or, enjoy a little Grape Soda in the tub and soak in a hot bath while immersing yourself in a good book. Phenotype Hybrid Cross phenotype of Tahoe OG Kush Notes Herbal, citrus, spicy, sweet Earthy, Herbal, Spicy"

attributes.name: Bloom | 0.5g Live Surf | Gruntz
attributes.body: "Gruntz Gruntz produces an uplifting sensation that leaves consumers feeling focused, tingly, and euphoric. This strain is ideal for daytime hours or as a wake and bake strain. Gruntz features a tropical flavor profile, with undertones of grapefruit and chemicals. Phenotype Hybrid Cross Gelato and Zkittlez Notes Grapefruit, Tropical, Gassy"

attributes.name: Bloom | 0.5g Live Surf | Lemon Jack
attributes.body: "Lemon Jack Lemon Jack is refreshing, fragrant and energizing. The flavor notes are dominated by a zested lemon peel followed by a strong scent of pine. The effect is Iike a mild dose of adrenaline; buzzy but incredibly productive when focused. Phenotype Sativa Cross Jack Herer x Lemon Kush Notes Lemon Zest, Bergamot, Mountain Pine"

attributes.name: Bloom | 0.5g Live Surf | Space Dust
attributes.body: "Space Dust Space Dust, an indica leaning hybrid, will take you there and back. Created by crossing Pink 2.0 and Locktite, this powerful strain has scents and flavors of sour citrus and sweet candy, accented by spicy herbals flavors by engulf with every hit. Expect a heavy-handed, hazy euphoric feeling, all while uplifting and relaxing. Phenotype Hybird Cross Pink 2.0 x Locktite Notes Sour citrus, Berries, Spice "
